'Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; text-align: center; background: url(http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png) 0% 22px no-repeat;">&ldquo;Education is the most powerful weapon which you can use to change the world.&rdquo;</h1>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">The UFCW is about workers coming together to build better lives for themselves.&nbsp; It is about creating opportunity.&nbsp; That is why each year the UFCW awards several scholarships of up to $1,000 each to UFCW members or their unmarried dependents under the age of 20.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="margin: 15px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 1.125em; font-style: inherit; font-weight: 600; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1em; text-align: center;"><a href="http://ufcw5.org/?page_id=2320" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(60, 90, 152); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">Click here to learn how you can apply online.</a></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '43ec517d68b6edd3015b3edc9a11367b.png', '2015-03-24 15:07:05', '3.2', 1, '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1);
