(578, 'Many Faces, One Voice', '<p><img alt="" src="http://www.ufcw.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/capitolsteps-300x225.jpg" style="width: 280px; height: 210px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div id="hdr" style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(0, 37, 87); font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow: hidden; background: rgb(0, 73, 144);">\r\n<header class="wrapper" id="hdr-content" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none; max-width: 980px;">\r\n<h1 class="pagetitle" style="margin: 0px 12px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); float: left;">United Latinos of UFCW</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="post" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="entry" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<h2 style="margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background-image: url(http://www.ufcwaction.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 22px; background-repeat: no-repeat;">Political Priorities for the United Latinos</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul style="padding-right: 0px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; margin: 5px 0px !important; padding-left: 5px !important; list-style-position: outside !important;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 3px 0px 0px !important; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px !important; list-style: none !important; background: url(http://laborvote.weebly.com/files/theme/bullet.png?1413325694) 0px 9px no-repeat;">To increase political involvement among the latino membership of the various UFCW&nbsp;Unions<a href="http://www.afl-cio.org/" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(3, 112, 234);" target="mainFrame" title="">&nbsp;</a>across North America.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 3px 0px 0px !important; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px !important; list-style: none !important; background: url(http://laborvote.weebly.com/files/theme/bullet.png?1413325694) 0px 9px no-repeat;">To inform and educate working Latinos by providing them information from various sources.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 3px 0px 0px !important; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px !important; list-style: none !important; background: url(http://laborvote.weebly.com/files/theme/bullet.png?1413325694) 0px 9px no-repeat;">To create a resource for historical, current<a href="http://www.laborvote.com/current.htm" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(3, 112, 234);" target="mainFrame" title="">&nbsp;</a>and future<a href="http://www.laborvote.com/future.htm" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(3, 112, 234);" target="mainFrame" title="">&nbsp;</a>issues that directly and indirectly impact working Latino families.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 3px 0px 0px !important; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px !important; list-style: none !important; background: url(http://laborvote.weebly.com/files/theme/bullet.png?1413325694) 0px 9px no-repeat;">To focus on issues that directly affect the lives of our Latino members, working families and residents of our&nbsp;communities.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 3px 0px 0px !important; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px !important; list-style: none !important; background: url(http://laborvote.weebly.com/files/theme/bullet.png?1413325694) 0px 9px no-repeat;">To register to vote as many working Latino families as possible in an effort to support and further the causes of those who Labor for a living.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '2015-03-23 09:38:03', '33.1', 2, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0),
(579, 'Volunteer to Help', '<p><img alt="" src="http://www.ufcwunitedlatinos.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/10305046_10204010125637158_436701657232284301_n4.jpg" style="width: 280px; height: 165px;" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div id="hdr" style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(0, 37, 87); font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; overflow: hidden; background: rgb(0, 73, 144);">\r\n<header class="wrapper" id="hdr-content" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; outline: none; max-width: 980px;">\r\n<h1 class="pagetitle" style="line-height: 1em; margin: 0px 12px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); float: left;">United Latinos of UFCW</h1>\r\n</header>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="post" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<div class="entry" style="margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px 0px 1.5em; outline: none; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\r\n<h2 style="line-height: 1em; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 18px 0px 10px 20px; outline: none; border-width: 10px 0px 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-top-color: rgb(255, 196, 37); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 73, 144); font-family: proxima-nova-condensed, proxima-nova, ''Proxima Nova'', HelveticaNeue, ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 1.875em; vertical-align: baseline; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(0, 73, 144); min-height: 30px; background-image: url(http://www.ufcwaction.org/wp-content/themes/ufcw/images/bg_hdr.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 0% 22px; background-repeat: no-repeat;">We are here to help!</h2>\r\n\r\n<div><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22.3999996185303px;">United Latinos will assist UFCW Regions, Local Unions and other organizations in their efforts to communicate, organize and servicing Latino members. We help with basic Spanish translations, Spanish press conferences and rallies, organizing (blitz and campaigns), immigration issues, help in training programs for Latino workers, voter registration, GOTV, electing candidates, etc.</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22.3999996185303px;">The United Latinos is the face and the voice of the UFCW when we need to reach Latino working men and women.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: ''Open Sans'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22.3999996185303px;">To get involved in an area near you, please email us at <a href="mailto:dgarcia@ufcw5.org?subject=Volunteer%20to%20Help%20the%20United%20Latinos">dgarcia@ufcw5.org</a> and we will help!</strong></p>\r\n', '', '2015-03-23 09:40:22', '33.2', 2, '', '', '', '', '', NULL, 0),
(580, 'Executive action to provide relief to immigrant workers, families, and communities', '<div style="font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; line-height: 19px;">\r\n<div dir="ltr">President Obamas executive action to provide relief to immigrant workers, families, and communities<span data-mce-style="color: #1f497d;" style="color: rgb(31, 73, 125);">&nbsp;</span>is a victory for the UFCW, our members, and the entire nation<span data-mce-style="color: #1f497d;" style="color: rgb(31, 73, 125);">.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>While executive action is not a substitute for comprehensive immigration reform, it is a step in the right direction and will directly impact tens of thousands of our members.&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div dir="ltr">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div dir="ltr"><img alt="" src="http://media2.s-nbcnews.com/i/newscms/2014_47/777911/141120-obama-immigration-jms-2024_e9cd4e9d2cf7830c7f272be73e467ff0.jpg" style="width: 280px; height: 187px;" /></div>\r\n\r\n<div dir="ltr">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div dir="ltr">A UFCW working group made up of key staff from the Civil Rights and Community Action, Food Processing, Packing, and Manufacturing, Legislative and Political, Legal, and Communications Departments is developing a plan to work with you to help eligible members access these newly expanded programs. This will include a comprehensive checklist of what is needed, worksite flyers, and other important resources.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="font-family: Georgia, ''Times New Roman'', ''Bitstream Charter'', Times, serif; line-height: 19px;">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Attached is the&nbsp;<span data-mce-style="color: #00ccff;" style="color: rgb(0, 204, 255);"><a data-mce-="" href="http://www.ufcwunitedlatinos.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Immigration-Executive-Action-Local-Union-Fact-Sheet.pdf" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(237, 129, 55);"><span data-mce-style="color: #00ccff;" style="color: rgb(0, 204, 255);">fact sheet</span></a>&nbsp;</span>sheet for your local union officers and staff explaining what the President&rsquo;s actions entail&nbsp;and their timeline for implementation.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n', '', '2015-03-25 17:09:54', '34', 2, '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0),
